<FIRST>r a PM-BoxOffice     10-25 0379</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Box Office,0394</SECOND>
<HEAD>`Halloween' Returns To Scare More Money From Moviegoers</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By RICHARD DE ATLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>HOLLYWOOD (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
