ada </LOCATION>. <ORGANIZATION> Delchamps </ORGANIZATION> had sales of about $ 700 million last year and has 103 stores in <LOCATION> Alabama </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Mississippi </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Florida </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Louisiana </LOCATION>, and six liquor stores.
